item.title: Need help, how do u make a command to tele u somewhere
item.dc:creator: @gunztheduel gunztheduel
item.description:
@gunztheduel wrote:

Here it is -

if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("COMMANDNAME")) { teleportToX = X COORD; teleportToY = Y COORD; }

Change COMMANDNAME to what you want the command name to be. And change the X and Y coord to what you want it to be.[br][size=1]Posted on: May 27, 2007, 12:48:55 AM[/size][hr]Just find where all your commands are in client.java and paste in between a command.
